tutorial.whatIsFlag:
Through offensive and defensive confrontations, program analysis, etc., the participating teams are the first to obtain a string or other content in a certain format from the competition environment given by the organizer, and submit it to the organizer to win points. 
For convenience of naming, we call such content "Flag". 
The general format of Flag is a uniform starting name plus curly brackets, such as flag{hello_world} or moectf{welcome!}
